The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning. Specifically, the paper focuses on analyzing and understanding the features learned by Deep Q-networks (DQNs) in a non-blind manner. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the paper deals with image-based Atari2600 games. Additionally, since the paper discusses the optimization of deep neural networks, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a likely category. Finally, since the paper deals with the control of systems, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely but still possible category.
